name: Unidentified dead man
description: In the photo, the unidentified dead man was predicted to have died less than a month ago because his skin was in good condition when found. But instead of his eyes that were completely vanished, there were dark wells that seemed black and infinitely deep. These "eyes" made me think about the things that might have happened to the unidentified dead man. Because I could read the emotion he was experiencing the moment he died. The unidentified dead man had forgiven. He accepted what was going to happen to him.
